{"arkId":"cl010097079","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010097079","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"Tabati\u00e8re","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Tabati\u00e8re"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XVI (1774-1792) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1763 - 1770","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1763,"endYear":1770,"imprecision":"vers","text":"2e moiti\u00e9 du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Neuber, Johann Christian","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1732","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1808","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q1519858"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 63","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"accessoire personnel, bo\u00eete, \u00e9tui","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Tabati\u00e8re en or de forme rectangulaire, incrust\u00e9e de cabochons d\u0027agate. Faces cisel\u00e9es en bas-relief d\u0027ors de quatre couleurs (jaune, rose, vert, blanc) et de bouquets de fleurs encadrant 83 m\u00e9daillons ovales tous surmont\u00e9s d\u0027un num\u00e9ro en cartouche, de 1 \u00e0 83. Les m\u00e9daillons contiennent des plaques convexes d\u0027agate, de jaspe, de cornaline, d\u0027onyx ou encore d\u0027am\u00e9thyste. Bordure d\u0027encadrement en or grav\u00e9 de filets dentel\u00e9s. Doublure en or.\r\nSur le couvercle : 18 pierres fines et transparantes, incluses dans des cartouches num\u00e9rot\u00e9s de A \u00e0 Q. \r\nSur la plaque du dessous : deux inventaires manuscrits, en allemand et en fran\u00e7ais, faits en carton recouvert de satin rose, l\u0027appellation des pierres et num\u00e9ro de renvoi y figurent. \r\nInventaire intitul\u00e9 \u0022Cabinet de pierres contenant toutes les sortes de pierres les plus belles et les mieux choisies, de Jaspe, de Vermeille, de Topas, d\u0027Ametiste, d\u0027Agate et encore d\u0027autres pierres pr\u00e9cieuses qui se trouvent en Saxe, tr\u00e8s exactement marqu\u00e9es de lettres et de chiffres pour en apprendre leurs noms. Compos\u00e9 par Jean Chr\u00e9tien Neuber \u00e0 Dresde\u0022","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ;  (Aucun)\r ; Signature : \r ; \u0022Neuber \u00e0 Dresde\u0022 (Sur la gorge, de face)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"3,9","displayDimension":"3,9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"8","displayDimension":"8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"5,8","displayDimension":"5,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : agate\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or","placeOfCreation":"Dresde (Allemagne-\u003ESaxe)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Th\u00e9odore Dablin, legs en 1861 ; vol\u00e9e au mus\u00e9e Cognacq-Jay, Paris, le 20 novembre 2024.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Dablin, Th\u00e9odore","note":"","role":", Collectionneur ; Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du legs","value":"1861","startYear":1861,"endYear":1861}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temp